fuse
   fuse legs of a Tensor.

SYNOPSIS

   Result=T.fuse.ith
   Result=T.fuse.(/i1,i2/)
   
   type(Tensor)     Result,T
   integer          ith,i1,i2


NOTE

   T.fuse.ith is the same as T%fuse(ith) and T.fuse.(/i1,i2/) is the same as T%fuse(i1,i2), see the example in 
   Type bound procedres of fuse
